| Name | Trigger |
|---|---|
{{ for wf in ent_group.items | array.sort 'name' -}}
| {{ wf.name }} | {{ wf | classic_trigger }} |
{{ end }}
{{ end -}}
{{ end }}

### Cloud Flows

